# ==========================================================================
# docker/backup/pgpass  (DO NOT COMMIT)
#
# Purpose:
# - Prevent any interactive password prompt when pgBackRest connects to Postgres.
#
# Format:
#   hostname:port:database:username:password
#
# Notes:
# - Must be chmod 0600 or libpq will ignore it.
# - Using wildcards avoids mismatches (TCP host vs local unix socket).
# ==========================================================================

